                     <colophon xml:lang="gez" xml:id="coloph1">
                        <locus from="58vb" to="59r"/>
                        ዝመጽሓፍ፡ ዘአባ፡ ገብረ፡ ሕይወት፡ ዘአጥረዩ፡ በንዋዩ፡ ዘሠረቆ፡ ወዘፈሐቆ፡ ውጉዘ፡ ለይኩን፨ በ፲፻፳፫ዓመተ፡ ምሕረት፨ ወወሀባ፡ ለኪዳነ፡ ምሕረት፡ ማየ፡
                        አንበሳ፡ ከመ፡ ይኩኖ፡ መርሃ፡ ለመንግሥተ፡ ሰማያት፨
                        <note>It states that <persName role="donor" ref="PRS15436GabraHeywat"><roleName type="title">ʾAbbā</roleName> Gabra Ḥǝywat</persName> bought the manuscript with his money and donated it to the monastery of <placeName ref="INS0174MAKM">Māy ʾAnbasā</placeName> 
                          in 1930/31 A.D. (the date is misspelled, but can be reconstructed to <date calendar="ethiopian" when-custom="1923" notBefore="1930" notAfter="1931">the year of
                              mercy 1923, that is, 1930/31</date>).
                       </note></colophon>
                  </msItem>
